# LDU Grant Ops — Frontend Design System

## Stack
- **Next.js 14** App Router, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS
- **Fonts:** Orbitron (display/numbers), Inter (body)
- **Icons:** Custom pixel-art SVG via `<PixelIcon name="…" />` — NO emojis, NO lucide-react

## Color Palette
```
Page background:  #1565e8  (royal blue + 24px pixel grid)
Card background:  #fffbf0  (warm cream)
Card alt:         #ffffff
Ink/borders:      #0a0a1a
Muted text:       #aaaacc
```

