## Entity Color System (lib/entities.ts)
Apply consistently to every card as a left border stripe + entity chip:
| Entity            | Color   | Background |
|-------------------|---------|------------|
| LDU (501c3)       | #1565e8 | #dbeafe    |
| Studio WELEH      | #ff1e78 | #ffe0f0    |
| Gorilla Rx        | #00a83a | #d1fae5    |
| Farm Entity       | #ff6b00 | #fde68a    |
| Kika Keith        | #7c3aed | #ede9fe    |

Always import `getEntityStyle` from `@/lib/entities`.

